        "id": "D",
        "text": "5/4"
      },
      {
        "id": "E",
        "text": "None of these"
      }
    ],
    "answer": "C",
    "explanation": "Let the required fraction be x. Then, 1/x - x = 9/20\n(1 - x^2) / x = 9/20\n20 - 20x^2 = 9x\n20x^2 + 9x - 20 = 0\n20x^2 + 25x - 16x - 20 = 0\n5x (4x + 5) - 4 (4x + 5) = 0\n(4x + 5) (5x - 4) = 0\nx = 4/5"
  },
